10
00:00:16,309 --> 00:00:18,269
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Leonard Bailey's alibi
witness is dead.</b></i></font>

11
00:00:18,353 --> 00:00:19,729
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That doesn't mean
